{"title":"皮鞭变绞索","authors":["禾君"],"dates":[{"year":1958,"month":9,"day":16}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"皮鞭变绞索"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"禾君"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"金元鞭头系，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"皮鞭手中握。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"金元要把“鱼”钓，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"皮鞭要把人吓。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人民力量大如山，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人民眼睛明似火。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"吓也吓不倒，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"骗也骗不着。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"皮鞭满天舞，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"好像着了魔，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"落到自己脖子上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"皮鞭忽然变绞索。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"越拉索越紧，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"越缠圈越多。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这才是——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"自作自己受，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"弄巧反成拙！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（附图片）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"绞索套在脖子上"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"阿勃拉莫夫"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（原载苏联“真理报”）"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":3,"page_end":3}